      <title>马克龙提前大选导致法国商业信心下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/french-business-confidences-slumped-during-turbulent-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于企业考虑到提前选举带来的动荡使法国陷入不确定的政治未来，法国企业信心跌至新冠疫情以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/french-business-confidences-slumped-during-turbulent-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:45:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
